; Coverage test for annotate.cc: fixated total cost annotations with {{=}}
; Exercises annotate.cc parsing {{}} total cost annotations
; and ANNOTATION_PRICE_NOT_PER_UNIT flag handling.
; Auto-balancing produces the same annotated commodity in both accounts.

2024/01/01 Buy at fixated total cost
    Assets:Brokerage    10 AAPL {{=$1500.00}}
    Assets:Checking

P 2024/03/01 AAPL $200.00

test bal --lots -> 0
                   0  Assets
  10 AAPL {=$150.00}    Brokerage
 -10 AAPL {=$150.00}    Checking
--------------------
                   0
end test
